{"tid":2292981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建制研規範立法會議員開會Dress code　T恤、短褲將成絕唱","createTime":"2020-11-20T02:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T02:39:14.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe4af76779ae4b6f0f21f681c6e9219aadad500","tid":2292981,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"民主派議員上周宣布總辭後，建制派成為議會主角，一舉一動都備受關注。建制派早前已率先在議事規則委員會上動議修改《內務守則》，包括將立法會大會上傳召官員的議案排在議員無約束力議案之後，減低泛民提出傳召官員的機會。<br />\n<br />\n建制派班長廖長江上周亦指，不會因為民主派總辭而改變原有修改《議事規則》的計劃。據悉，建制派核心近日除了密鑼緊鼓撰寫修改的詳細內容外，有議員更建議應趁機「食住上」，正醞釀進一步規範議員的行為及衣著，包括禁止議員穿著T恤、短褲等出席會議。至於如何執行，關鍵全繫於立法會主席梁君彥<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/551106/%E6%94%BF%E5%9C%88%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%A0%94%E8%A6%8F%E7%AF%84%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83dress-code-t%E6%81%A4-%E7%9F%AD%E8%A4%B2%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E7%B5%95%E5%94%B1?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;fbclid=IwAR1gHsNLlJcfSdH-i1XVjdX4LaHn8iTpXG_RGtTwAoePrz4FI3iwhP2QBGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F551106%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%259C%2588%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A6%258F%25E7%25AF%2584%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583dress-code-t%25E6%2581%25A4-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E8%25A4%25B2%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2594%25B1%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost%26utm_campaign%3Dnews%26fbclid%3DIwAR1gHsNLlJcfSdH-i1XVjdX4LaHn8iTpXG_RGtTwAoePrz4FI3iwhP2QBGI&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=7fbbe7b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/551106/%E6%94%BF%E5%9C%88%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E7%A0%94%E8%A6%8F%E7%AF%84%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83dress-code-t%E6%81%A4-%E7%9F%AD%E8%A4%B2%E5%B0%87%E6%88%90%E7%B5%95%E5%94%B1?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost&amp;ut